{"tid":1864251,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得讀大學其實真係好大壓力","createTime":"2020-02-05T13:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T00:40:30.000Z","uid":133304,"like":46,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"acb7310990e0562d209c25947459d20e4d29a109","tid":1864251,"uid":133304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"就嚟讀master<br />\n窮jj bachelor時邊做pt邊返學，個個sem都返一至五加埋份週末返嘅pt已經覺得好似成日都唞唔到氣咁；自己忙加上社交圈子啲人成日夾唔到時間見，而我又係好需要間唔中見下朋友嘅人嚟，有時真係覺得情緒都幾壓抑。<br />\n有時做功課好老實講已經好努力去meet啲criteria但最後出嚟個分都係事與願違，或者真係做極都唔係好知做緊乜而tutor係比唔到真係可以支援我嘅指引<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做實習又要meet好多嘅expectation，行每步路都要好小心好謹慎咁。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時真係諗起返學都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日覺得搵定精神科好啲，我覺得遲早壓力大到會痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人同我一樣如題咁諗？"},{"pid":"40f4baf7ed3be8f3cc08f3e5b93b49d37673f3be","tid":1864251,"uid":73959,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n究竟要幾大壓力先至會覺得大壓力但係又要去讀Master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c55a2fc114731cb6812f8ffac23ade40bc340cc","tid":1864251,"uid":133304,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"40f4baf7ed3be8f3cc08f3e5b93b49d37673f3be","tid":1864251,"uid":73959,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n究竟要幾大壓力先至會覺得大壓力但係又要去讀Master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"我嗰科要讀埋master先出路穩定啲"},{"pid":"4c50fb1ce193d97d9753d93d59ba98bb5dd1047a","tid":1864251,"uid":187399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"返學仲返埋part time 好犀利<br />\n淨係讀書就用好多時間同精神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c0a05ad4934dd92fc30d83f3847abb